{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"84efcb59f8","title":"在八届十中全会上对工业支援农业的指示","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"469f5b9577","index":0,"year":1962,"month":7,"day":24,"articleId":"84efcb59f8"}],"tags":[{"id":"2d13338754","name":"指示","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"c20d333791","name":"关键人物文稿","type":"文稿大类"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"wansui5","name":"毛泽东思想万岁(1961-1968卷)","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"未知","files":"/books/wansui5a.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"wansui5":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"3860bfed59","type":"title","text":"在八届十中全会上对工业支援农业的指示","index":0,"publicationId":"wansui5","articleId":"84efcb59f8"},{"id":"e9322b1296","type":"paragraph","text":"（北戴河记录稿）","index":1,"publicationId":"wansui5","articleId":"84efcb59f8"},{"id":"2dc124bcda","type":"paragraph","text":"〔在谈到坚持集体化方向，工业支援农业时说〕：搞了四年，以农业为基础的方针不大自觉，不大愿意。巩固集体经济有两方面：一是政策，二是支援农业。从长远来说是农业的技术改造，总的是如何搞社会主义建设的问题。","index":2,"publicationId":"wansui5","articleId":"84efcb59f8"},{"id":"8c58658a31","type":"paragraph","text":"科学的研究，没有抓农业。科学院党组书记说：科学院是搞尖端的。","index":3,"publicationId":"wansui5","articleId":"84efcb59f8"},{"id":"4d135f88ef","type":"paragraph","text":"要抓农业技术改造。","index":4,"publicationId":"wansui5","articleId":"84efcb59f8"},{"id":"af539ae8d8","type":"paragraph","text":"民主与集中，集中与分散，分散主义首先是中央（指综合部门）。农业机械化要搞个文件，二十五年左右实现机械化，同时实现工业化。有的同志在困难面前躺下。是消极好，还是鼓足干劲好？是单干，还是集体好，要提起注意。","index":5,"publicationId":"wansui5","articleId":"84efcb59f8"},{"id":"02a893af73","type":"paragraph","text":"对困难发生消极情绪是不是思想问题？","index":6,"publicationId":"wansui5","articleId":"84efcb59f8"},{"id":"ef1ed937a5","type":"paragraph","text":"计委、经委、工交各部要加强支援农业。要抓紧改，这是机会，还来得及。","index":7,"publicationId":"wansui5","articleId":"84efcb59f8"},{"id":"07797530f5","type":"paragraph","text":"计委搞两个文件：支援农业的报告，三个部分：方向，面向农业，支援农业的方针。","index":8,"publicationId":"wansui5","articleId":"84efcb59f8"}],"page":{"id":"bd308bded2","publicationId":"wansui5","articleId":"84efcb59f8","start":85,"end":85}}}},"__N_SSG":true}